## hostname: bm-xserve01
## uname: Darwin bm-xserve01.mozilla.org 8.5.0 Darwin Kernel Version 8.5.0: Sun Jan 22 10:38:46 PST 2006; root:xnu-792.6.61.obj~1/RELEASE_PPC Power Macintosh powerpc
